==Pasiknangan (Sports/Athletics)==
{{main|Letran Knights}}
[[Image:Knightslogo.jpg|right|125px|The Letran athletics logo]]Kayanib ya ing Letran king [[National Collegiate Athletic Association (Philippines)|National Collegiate Athletic Association]] manibat anyang 1928 anggang 1932, at manibat kanitang 1936.

Makyabe ya ing Colegio king [[NCAA Philippines Basketball Championship|basketball]], [[NCAA Philippines Volleyball Championship|volleyball]], [[NCAA Philippines Football Championship|football (soccer)]], [[NCAA Philippines Track and Field Championship|track and field]], [[NCAA Philippines Taekwondo Championship|taekwondo]] ampo king [[NCAA Philippines Tennis Championship|lawn tennis]]. Ing aus da kareng varsity teams, ''Letran Knights'' (seniors division), ''Squires'' (juniors division) at ''Lady Knights'' (babai)

The seniors basketball team is the most successful team in the NCAA. Since joining in the 1928-29 season, the Knights have won a total of sixteen titles, the most in NCAA seniors basketball. The most recent championship came in the [[2005 NCAA Philippines Basketball Playoffs|2005 tournament]], with a record of 13-1 in the eliminations and 3-1 in the playoffs (2-1 in the Finals) for an overall record of 16-2.
Matagumpe yang dili ing seniors basketball team king NCAA. Manibat anyang mikyabe ya kanitang 1928-29, labing anam a titulu ing karelang simbut, ing maragul diling bilang king NCAA. Tawli yang meging campiun ketang [[w:2005 NCAA Philippines Basketball Playoffs|2005 tournament]], nung nu mika record yang 13-1 king eliminations at 3-1 king playoffs (2-1 king finals), o metung a pangkabilugan a record a 16-2.

The staple cheer is ''Arriba Letran!'' (English: "Fly high Letran"). Several cheers of the Colegio were among of the first cheers to be used in the NCAA. The team supporters are known as ''Dugong Arriba'' (Arriba blooded).
Ing staple cheer yapin ing ''Arriba Letran!'' (Kapampangan: "Mibabo ka Letran"). Deng mapilan a cheer ning Colegio ing metung kareng minunang megamit king NCAA. Deng kakampi ning team awsan da no mang ''Dugong Arriba'' (dayang Arriba).
Their most prominent rivals are the [[De La Salle University-Manila|De La Salle]] Green Archers (before the Green Archers left the NCAA), [[San Sebastian Stags]] and the [[Mapua Cardinals]], their neighbor in Intramuros.
Deng masikan dang diling ka-rival ila pin deng [[De La Salle University-Manila|De La Salle]] Green Archers (bayu la meko king NCAA deng Green Archers), [[San Sebastian Stags]] ampo reng [[Mapua Cardinals]], deng kasiping dang bale king Intramuros.

